This is a demo project to create microservices
using Spring Boot, Kafka, Cassandra, MySQL and MongoDB

Order Service -- Kafka
Payment Service -- MySQL
    --FlywayDB (or just Flyway) is a database migration tool
    --that helps manage and automate version-controlled schema changes.
Product Catalog Service -- Cassandra
User Analytics Service -- Cassandra

healthcare-platform/
├── pom.xml                          (Parent POM)
├── common/
│   ├── pom.xml
│   └── src/main/java/com/healthcare/common/
│       └── events/
│           ├── OrderEvent.java
│           ├── PaymentEvent.java
│           └── ProductEvent.java
├── order-service/
│   ├── pom.xml
│   └── src/main/
│       ├── java/com/healthcare/orders/
│       │   ├── OrderApplication.java
│       │   ├── controller/OrderController.java
│       │   ├── model/Order.java
│       │   └── service/OrderService.java
│       └── resources/
│           ├── application.properties
│           └── kafka/
├── payment-service/                  (MySQL)
│   ├── pom.xml
│   └── src/main/
│       ├── java/com/healthcare/payments/
│       │   ├── PaymentApplication.java
│       │   ├── model/Payment.java
│       │   └── repository/PaymentRepository.java
│       └── resources/
│           ├── application.properties
│           └── db/migration/        (Flyway scripts)
├── catalog-service/                  (Cassandra)
│   ├── pom.xml
│   └── src/main/
│       ├── java/com/healthcare/catalog/
│       │   ├── CatalogApplication.java
│       │   ├── model/Product.java
│       │   └── repository/ProductRepository.java
│       └── resources/
│           ├── application.properties
│           └── cassandra/           (CQL scripts)
├── analytics-service/                (Cassandra)
│   ├── pom.xml
│   └── src/main/
│       ├── java/com/healthcare/analytics/
│       │   ├── AnalyticsApplication.java
│       │   ├── model/UserActivity.java
│       │   └── service/AnalyticsService.java
│       └── resources/
│           └── application.properties
└── api-gateway/
    ├── pom.xml
    └── src/main/
        ├── java/com/healthcare/gateway/
        └── resources/
            └── application.properties